import { Button, Form } from "semantic-ui-react";

const memeForm = () => (
  <Form>
    <Form.Field>
      <label>Meme Owner</label>
      <input placeholder="Enter your full name" />
    </Form.Field>
    <Form.Field>
      <label>Caption</label>
      <input placeholder="Be Creative with caption" />
    </Form.Field>
    <Form.Field>
      <label>Meme URL</label>
      <input placeholder="Enter URL of your meme here" />
    </Form.Field>
    <Button type="submit">Submit</Button>
  </Form>
);

export default memeForm
